N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 40.12 - Persons

State Regulations

Persons subject to or affected by this Part shall
be: (a) all producers as defined in
this Part; and
(b) all milk dealers
as defined in this Part who receive milk from producers. Notes
